            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20527537">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20527537/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p20527537-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 
真正恶俗的事物必然会显示出刻意虚饰、矫揉造作或欺骗性。不新鲜的食物是糟糕的，若餐馆刻意奉上不新鲜的食物，还要赋以“美食”之名，那就是恶俗了。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20527537/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-08-21 15:05</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p20527537-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
<blockquote><q>真正恶俗的事物必然会显示出刻意虚饰、矫揉造作或欺骗性。不新鲜的食物是糟糕的，若餐馆刻意奉上不新鲜的食物，还要赋以“美食”之名，那就是恶俗了。</q></blockquote>
